Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.30,0:00:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't even know if\Nthose memories are real.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.77,0:00:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What if I am a Galerian?
